##  mappings

map p change_mode   presentation
map [presentation]  <C-r> recolor
map [fullscreen]    <C-r> recolor

##  colors

set default-bg              "#1d1f21"
set completion-bg           "#1d1f21"
set completion-highlight-bg "#5f819d"
set inputbar-bg             "#1d1f21"
set inputbar-fg             "#5f819d"
set statusbar-bg            "#1d1f21"
set tabbar-focus-fg         "#5f819d"

